TITLE: Starting a Call with Existing Agent in Ultravox
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to initiate a call using a previously created agent ID, including the ability to pass customer context information to populate template variables.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fixie-ai/ultradox/blob/main/essentials/agents.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const startAgentCall = async (agentId) => {
  const response = await fetch(`https://api.ultravox.ai/api/agents/${agentId}/calls`, {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
      'Content-Type': 'application/json',
      'X-API-Key': 'your-api-key'
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({
      templateContext: {
        customerName: "Jane Smith"
      }
    })
  });

  return await response.json();
};
```

