TITLE: Creating an Ultravox Call for WebSockets in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to create a WebSocket-based call with the Ultravox API using JavaScript. It shows the POST request to initialize a call with specific parameters including system prompt, model, voice, and WebSocket-specific settings like input and output sample rates.
