TITLE: Creating an API Call with Specific Ultravox Model in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to specify a model when creating a call to the Ultravox API. The example shows the request body format that includes the system prompt and model specification.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fixie-ai/ultradox/blob/main/availablemodels.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
