TITLE: File Upload Command for Corpus Source
DESCRIPTION: Curl command for uploading a text file to the corpus storage using a pre-signed URL.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fixie-ai/ultradox/blob/main/essentials/rag.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
FILE_PATH="/path/to/your/file"
UPLOAD_URL="https://storage.googleapis.com/fixie-ultravox-prod/..."

curl -X PUT \
  -H "Content-Type: text/plain" \
  --data-binary @"$FILE_PATH" \
  "$UPLOAD_URL"
```

